{"tid":1042892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果可以比你時光倒流翻小學畢業，可以點改變世界","createTime":"2019-03-02T00:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T04:07:59.000Z","uid":213328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2bacd8d22f3d77e90f5873467898a271a7cfa542","tid":1042892,"uid":213328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T00:18:06.000Z","msg":"畀你即刻帶著依家嘅意識同記憶翻去你啱啱小學畢業嗰陣。<br />\n但係冇時間比你準備，即喺你唔可以記低六合彩歷屆開獎號碼之類。點先可以令自己嘅一生過得最成功。<br />\n<br />\n好似有啲難度。勸老豆老母all in買樓等升值佢哋一定唔會信。如果靠讀書屈機都唔一定成功，食老本食到中六中七/大學應該都會開始覺得力有不逮。就算真係比你靠神童status入到MIT,哈佛都會比真嘅天才屈機，最後on99攞住張cert畢業，又喺要出嚟打工，最多起薪點高幾千蚊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6eb70131cf77c4692502924b6bfec2c1104e7c","tid":1042892,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T00:19:05.000Z","msg":"改變世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你邊位啊"},{"pid":"7738329effbed85e35230d1664f60650468d8196","tid":1042892,"uid":35746,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T00:20:27.000Z","msg":"歷屆 聯賽 歐聯 世盃冠軍"},{"pid":"d983726759b39194126d4bb5c5816b349b8a833a","tid":1042892,"uid":59192,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T00:24:15.000Z","msg":"德國巴西7:1"},{"pid":"9859091c26ccf68639765be72b682f9580bd9e4c","tid":1042892,"uid":213328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a6eb70131cf77c4692502924b6bfec2c1104e7c","tid":1042892,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T00:19:05.000Z","msg":"改變世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你邊位啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T00:25:06.000Z","msg":"比你穿越埋時間都淨係做中產好唔抵"},{"pid":"4df30c60bff3783a921606ce3936ff28f8c0def3","tid":1042892,"uid":213328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7738329effbed85e35230d1664f60650468d8196","tid":1042892,"uid":35746,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T00:20:27.000Z","msg":"歷屆 聯賽 歐聯 世盃冠軍"